    <h1>The Rimaeri</h1>
    <p class="lede">The Rimaeri are the people of the Rim. Outsiders may call them Rimmers, but among themselves they are Rimaeri.</p>
    <p>Their identity is shaped by border life, movement, memory, fairness, and practical ways of living between worlds that do not always match each other neatly.</p>
    <p>They are shaped by routes, weather, exchange, shared knowledge, and the practical work of living where crossing matters. Fairness, memory, and rhythm can carry as much weight as possession or fixed boundaries.</p>
    <p>Rimaeri life is not one single type of life. Families, places, duties, and ways of remembering can differ, while still holding a shared sense of belonging to the Rim.</p>
